cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.LG 

The paper discusses access control policies and algorithms for mining them, which are relevant to computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). The use of object-oriented extensions and path expressions suggests a software engineering (cs.SE) aspect to the work. The use of heuristics and evolutionary algorithms suggests an artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) aspect to the work.
